data.description: This is the one for you! Sitting on one of the largest lots in the neighborhood. Equipped with a new privacy fence and extended gate that leads you to plenty of space to enjoy the large backyard that includes a trampoline and playset that the owner is leaving for you! Take a glance at the brand-new roof installed (Oct 2023) and the storm cellar that is there for added piece of mind during any storm. Inside you will notice the freshly painted walls/trim throughout making it bright and inviting.  You will enjoy the versatility of this split floorplan with 4 oversized bedrooms that include new carpet and ample amounts of closet space. The living room/kitchen are an open concept leaving plenty of space to entertain. If that is not space to relax then grab your coffee and blanket enjoy your sunroom full of natural light with each window having window seats (and storage) for added comfort. We can't forget about the garage with its new interior doors, fresh paint and new epoxied floors!
